{
  "stem": "19895.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 55.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that death march took us through towns, which, which I recall were the football field of [HUNGARIAN] and through towns which-- [HUNGARIAN]-- a long name, but it's a town's name-- where the town people were on the streets, seeing this pitiful sight of people with their Jewish stars and just marching on, totally disorderly, by guards making sure that nobody escapes.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And as the days went on, the stretch of that group was just drawn out further and further.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were trying to keep us marching faster.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And exhaustion to place, and people were collapsing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, and, they were-- when somebody collapsed, they just shot the person on the site.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And more and more of this instant shooting, so nobody dared to fall down and, and, and try to do anything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Nevertheless, after about three days, somehow I had some urge of trying to escape.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And during the night, when we were coming out from [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a town called [HUNGARIAN], we were sleeping on, on transportation ships, which-- coal was transported on the rivers.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were all herded into the belly of those transportation ships.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And people on each other were just sleeping there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And again, during the night, if anybody had some needs of emptying his bowel or, or urine, it just happened on the scene.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The smell was foul and sick and awful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "When we were coming out and continuing the march, in that confusion, I escaped.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I started my march, back towards Budapest on the highway in the opposite direction.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And a transportation, a truck came by.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And being a 16-year-old little boy, I motioned and he just take me on, didn't ask questions.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And-- seen my yellow star but didn't ask questions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I said I want to go to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
